<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4b5563;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 24px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 48px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
        50% { opacity: 0.8; }
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .header-icon {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 0 auto 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 32px;
        background: white;
      }

      .content h2 {
        color: #1f2937;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-info {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
        border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-address {
        color: #2563eb;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .security-notice {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fed7aa 100%);
        border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-left: 6px solid #f59e0b;
        position: relative;
      }

      .security-notice::before {
        content: '🔒';
        position: absolute;
        top: -12px;
        left: 24px;
        background: #f59e0b;
        color: white;
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .security-notice h3 {
        color: #92400e;
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .security-notice p {
        color: #92400e;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
      }

      .link-fallback {
        background: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 16px 0;
        word-break: break-all;
      }

      .link-fallback-label {
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .link-fallback-url {
        color: #2563eb;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .expiry-notice {
        background: #fef3c7;
        border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      }

      .expiry-notice h3 {
        color: #92400e;
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .expiry-notice p {
        color: #92400e;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
        background: #f9fafb;
        border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
      }

      .footer p {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 20px;
          border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 32px 24px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content h2 {
          font-size: 22px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-icon">🔑</div>
        <h1>Password Reset</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; color: #1f2937; margin: 24px 0;">
          We received a request to reset the password for your account.
        </p>

        <div class="email-info">
          <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #6b7280;">Password reset requested for:</p>
          <div class="email-address"><%= @resource.email %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
          <h3>Security Notice</h3>
          <p>If you didn't request this password reset, someone else may be trying to access your account. In that case, please ignore this email and consider updating your password for security.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; color: #1f2937; margin: 24px 0;">
          Click the button below to reset your password:
        </p>

        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="<%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %>" class="button">Reset My Password</a>
        </div>

        <div class="link-fallback">
          <div class="link-fallback-label">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</div>
          <div class="link-fallback-url"><%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-notice">
          <h3>⏰ Time Sensitive</h3>
          <p>This password reset link will expire in <strong>6 hours</strong> for security reasons.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">
          If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent because a password reset was requested for this account.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
